                    </li>
                </ul>
                <div class="mobile-menu">☰</div>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Main Landing Page -->
    <div id="landingPage">
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="container">
                <h1>Create Unforgettable Events</h1>
                <p>From intimate gatherings to large conferences, Eventify makes event creation simple, beautiful, and effective.</p>
                <div class="hero-buttons">
                    <a href="#" class="btn" id="create-event-btn" >Create Your Event</a>
                   
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Features Section -->
        <section class="features">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <h2>Everything You Need for Perfect Events</h2>
                    <p>Our platform provides all the tools to create, promote, and manage successful events.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="features-grid">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-edit"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Easy Event Setup</h3>
                        <p>Create beautiful event pages in minutes with our intuitive drag-and-drop builder.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-ticket-alt"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Smart Ticketing</h3>
                        <p>Set up multiple ticket types, manage capacity, and track sales in real-time.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Automated Communications</h3>
                        <p>Send personalized confirmations, reminders, and follow-ups automatically.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-chart-bar"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Analytics & Insights</h3>
                        <p>Track attendance, engagement, and revenue with comprehensive dashboards.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Secure Payments</h3>
                        <p>Accept payments safely with our PCI-compliant, encrypted payment processing.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Mobile Check-In</h3>
                        <p>Check guests in quickly with our mobile app and QR code scanning.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- How It Works Section -->
        <section class="how-it-works">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <h2>How It Works</h2>
                    <p>Creating your event is as easy as 1-2-3 with our streamlined process.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="steps">
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-number">1</div>
                        <h3>Set Up Your Event</h3>
                        <p>Add event details, customize your page, and set ticket options.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-number">2</div>
                        <h3>Promote & Sell</h3>
                        <p>Share your event page and start selling tickets to attendees.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-number">3</div>
                        <h3>Manage & Host</h3>
                        <p>Check in guests, engage attendees, and analyze your success.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Testimonials Section -->
        <section class="testimonials">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <h2>What Our Users Say</h2>
                    <p>Thousands of event organizers trust Eventify to create memorable experiences.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="testimonial-grid">
                    <div class="testimonial-card">
                        <div class="testimonial-content">
                            <p>"Eventify transformed how we organize our annual conference. The ticketing system is flawless and the analytics helped us understand our audience better."</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="testimonial-author">
                            <div class="author-avatar">JS</div>
                            <div class="author-info">
                                <h4>Jessica Smith</h4>
                                <p>Conference Organizer</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="testimonial-card">
                        <div class="testimonial-content">
                            <p>"I used to spend days setting up events. With Eventify, I can create a beautiful event page in under an hour. The mobile check-in feature is a game-changer!"</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="testimonial-author">
                            <div class="author-avatar">MR</div>
                            <div class="author-info">
                                <h4>Michael Rodriguez</h4>
                                <p>Wedding Planner</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="testimonial-card">
                        <div class="testimonial-content">
                            <p>"The automated communication features saved me so much time. My attendees love the personalized reminders and follow-ups. Highly recommended!"</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="testimonial-author">
                            <div class="author-avatar">AK</div>
                            <div class="author-info">
                                <h4>Amanda Kim</h4>
                                <p>Corporate Event Manager</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- CTA Section -->
        <section class="cta">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Ready to Create Your Next Event?</h2>
                <p>Join thousands of event organizers who trust Eventify to create memorable experiences.</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn" id="cta-create-event">Get Started For Free</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

    <!-- Event Creation Page -->
    <div class="event-creation-page" id="eventCreationPage">
        <div class="container">
            <a href="#" class="back-button" id="back-to-home">
                <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Back to Home
            </a>
            <div class="page-title">
                <h1>What would you like to do?</h1>
